# prose_translation = Just as people may resemble many colors and shapes, or imitate them—some through crafts and others through habits, and another group through voices—so also all the crafts we have established produce imitation and mimesis through melody, speech, and rhythm.
# literal_translation = And as that the people may resemble with colors and shapes many or they imitate that from where that some of them resemble by the crafts and imitate them, and some of them by the habits, and a folk other from them by the voices: likewise the crafts which we established: all of them bring by the imitation and the mimesis by the melody and the speech and the rhythm.
